value.content:
The keys() method of the Highlight interface is an alias for the values() method.

Highlight is a Set-like object, so this is similar to using Set.keys().

value.title: Syntax
value.content:
js

keys()

value.title: Return value
value.content: A new iterator object containing each Range object in the given Highlight, in insertion order.
